        eng: " Taking a deep breath slowly, I got up and organized my head. I headed to the small desk in the corner of the room and sat down. There were scattered documents on the desk. I was thinking something while organizing them one by one. 'Ahh, it's already this time of day...' The sky outside the window was dyed in a beautiful orange color at dusk. 'I should go soon.' After tidying up the documents on the desk, I stood up and left the room. The air outside the house was still a bit hot, but I felt comfortable with the evening breeze. When I started walking down the road in front of my house, I could see her figure a little ahead. She seemed to have something in her hand and her strides were getting bigger. 'Ahh, already' Thinking so, I ran to her and she had a big bouquet in her right hand. 'This...?' 'Umm... this is it!' She seemed a bit nervous but said with a smile and offered me the bouquet. 'It's your birthday today so...' Looking up at her face as if enchanted, I received it carefully and put it in my hands. 'Thank you...' With an emotional feeling, I embraced her cheeks with both hands. She also lowered her gaze with joy and smiled slightly.",
