        eng: "I was in a deep forest. As I was walking between the trees, I could see the wind blowing the leaves. There was a clear and blue air flowing, giving me a feeling of nostalgia. Suddenly, there was some movement. Suddenly, a small shadow flew out from between the trees. I instinctively stopped. The small shadow was standing at my feet. She was wearing hiking clothes. Her hair was also swaying in the wind and enveloped in the bright sunlight. 'Who are you?' When I asked, she asked me back in a small voice, 'What did you come to do in this forest?' 'Do you have a real reason?' I couldn't hide my slightly anxious feeling. 'The real reason... hmm... today is a special day,' I answered, and she slowly smiled. ",
